query:
SET @ccc_id = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name LIKE '%Contra Costa%' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1);

-- Trauma protocols

(@ccc_id, 'AT01', 'Trauma Assessment', 'Trauma', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Trauma Assessment. Primary and secondary survey.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
